text: Andrea Wolfer (born 16 December 1987) is a track and road cyclist from Switzerland. She represented her nation at the 2009 UCI Road World Championships and 2009 UCI Track Cycling World Championships. She competed in the points race and scratch event at the 2010 UCI Track Cycling World Championships.
